<i>noun</i>: 벌레 [벌레] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>벌레 [벌레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. worm; bug</dd><br>
<dd>곤충이나 기생충 등 몸 구조가 간단한 동물.</dd><br>
<dd>An animal whose body has a simple structure, such as an insect or parasite.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hard worker</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어떤 일을 지치지 않고 매우 열심히 하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A person who works very hard tirelessly to do something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>